snippet.title: Hellmouth Trailer
snippet.description: The devil’s gotta eat, but he’s particular about what he wants. Chef Butt and Chef Fluffy are rival chefs who duke it out over ingredients to cook their boss the best dish. Hellmouth is a two-player cooking/fighting game.
